# ============================================
# CRITICAL REMINDER
# ============================================
# This .gitignore prevents:
# ✅ GEMINI_API_KEY from being exposed
# ✅ EMAIL_PASS (Gmail password) from being exposed
# ✅ MongoDB credentials from being exposed
# ✅ JWT secrets from being exposed
# ✅ All environment variables from being exposed
# ✅ Python venv from being committed (500MB+)
# ✅ Node modules from being committed (400MB+)
#
# IF YOU ACCIDENTALLY COMMITTED SECRETS:
# 1. Regenerate API keys immediately at:
#    - https://aistudio.google.com/apikey (Gemini)
#    - https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords (Gmail)
# 2. Remove from git history:
#    git rm --cached .env server/.env hybrid_roadmap/.env
#    git commit -m "Remove secrets from version control"
# 3. Force push: git push --force-with-lease
